title: CSE: 2015-0911 - New Listing - BlackEagle Development Corp. (BDC)
text:
September 18, 2015 12:34 ET CSE: 2015-0911 - New Listing - BlackEagle Development Corp. (BDC) 
TORONTO, ONTARIO--(Marketwired - Sept. 18, 2015) - The common shares of BlackEagle Development Corp. have been approved for listing on the CSE. 
Listing and disclosure documents will be available at thecse.com Trading Date: September 21, 2015 Symbol: BDC ISIN: CA 092302 10 8 7 Boardlot: TBD 
BlackEagle Development is currently listed on the TSX Venture Exchange. 
If you have any questions or require further information, or to be removed from the mailing list please contact Listings at (416) 367-7340 or E-mail: Listings@thecse.com Contact Information
